<description>&lt;p&gt;失恋的人听什么歌？听什么歌都会深有感触。&lt;br/&gt;心底空荡荡的，连呼吸都是轻飘飘的。&lt;br/&gt;以前你爱我是真的，现在不爱我也是真的。&lt;br/&gt;人是会变的，这是《重庆森林》里最经典最精炼的一句话，我收了。&lt;br/&gt;所有的回忆、温暖、怀念，都是不甘心啊！&lt;br/&gt;不甘心又能如何？再相遇又能如何？再打一炮又能如何？&lt;br/&gt;回不去了！&lt;br/&gt;在下一位有缘人还未出现之前，独自品尝一下曲终人散的寂寞吧，这也是走心的代价。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/23012386.gif&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/23012386.gif&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22542679.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22542679.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22544393.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22544393.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22545622.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22545622.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/2255024.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/2255024.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22551154.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22551154.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22551715.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22551715.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22552726.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22552726.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22553489.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22553489.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/i/?i=u/20191122/22554541.jpg&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.com/u/20191122/22554541.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.yuoimg.